      <title>Vivendi 开始以 30 亿美元收购 MultiChoice</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/vivendi-s-offer-to-buy-multichoice-valued-at-3-billion-begins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[维旺迪 SE 旗下的 Canal+ 于今年 4 月首次宣布以每股 125 兰特的价格向 MultiChoice Group Ltd. 提出强制性全现金收购要约，该收购将于周三开始。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/vivendi-s-offer-to-buy-multichoice-valued-at-3-billion-begins</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 06:29:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台积电新任董事长重申人工智能助力 2024 年经济复苏的希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/tsmc-s-new-chairman-affirms-hopes-of-ai-fueled-2024-recovery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾半导体制造公司董事长魏哲家周二成为多年来首位同时担任董事长和首席执行官的人物，他重申了对人工智能发展将推动 2024 年行业复苏的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/tsmc-s-new-chairman-affirms-hopes-of-ai-fueled-2024-recovery</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 04:33:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英特尔首席执行官在 AI 芯片领导地位之争中回击英伟达</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/intel-ceo-fires-back-at-nvidia-in-battle-for-ai-chip-leadership</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英特尔公司首席执行官帕特·基辛格在台湾台北国际电脑展上发表演讲，介绍他认为有助于扭转市场份额落后于同行（包括人工智能领导者英伟达公司）的新产品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/intel-ceo-fires-back-at-nvidia-in-battle-for-ai-chip-leadership</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 04:09:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>解决熊市关键问题后，苹果对 2024 年的预期转为乐观</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/apple-turns-positive-for-2024-after-addressing-key-bear-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司 (Apple Inc.) 周一收盘时，今年股价报收于正值，这是市场对这家 iPhone 制造商的信心回升的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/apple-turns-positive-for-2024-after-addressing-key-bear-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 20:42:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>AI 加速器、AI PC 和 GameStop 的崛起 | 彭博科技</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/ai-accelerators-ai-pcs-and-gamestop-s-surge-bloomberg-technology</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的 Caroline Hyde 关注了 Nvidia 首席执行官黄仁勋，称该公司计划每年升级其 AI 加速器。此外，高通首席执行官讨论了 AI PC，而随着 Roaring Kitty 宣布持有该公司价值 1.16 亿美元的股份，GameStop 股价再次飙升。

（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/ai-accelerators-ai-pcs-and-gamestop-s-surge-bloomberg-technology</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 20:29:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TikTok 母公司聘请新法律总顾问，助力其与美国政府展开竞争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/bytedance-tiktok-hire-john-rogovin-as-general-counsel-amid-fight-with-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[TikTok 的母公司字节跳动有限公司已任命前华纳兄弟探索公司高管约翰·罗戈文 (John Rogovin) 为新的全球总法律顾问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/bytedance-tiktok-hire-john-rogovin-as-general-counsel-amid-fight-with-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 20:20:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国将出售 25 亿欧元德国电信股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/deutsche-telekom-investor-kfw-to-sell-2-5-billion-in-shares</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国出售了德国电信公司 (Deutsche Telekom AG) 价值 25 亿欧元（27 亿美元）的股份，这是资金短缺的政府为剥离部分公司资产而采取的一系列举措中的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/deutsche-telekom-investor-kfw-to-sell-2-5-billion-in-shares</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 16:04:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nvidia 和 AMD 争夺 AI 控制权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/jensen-huang-computex-keynote-nvidia-reveals-new-ai-software-and-services</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Nvidia Corp. 和 Advanced Micro Devices Inc. 的高管展示了推动全球人工智能发展繁荣的新一代芯片，加深了塑造人工智能设计和应用未来的竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/jensen-huang-computex-keynote-nvidia-reveals-new-ai-software-and-services</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 10:10:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Gill 重返 Reddit 彰显巨大赌注，GameStop 股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/gamestop-s-meme-moment-returns-again-with-gill-s-reddit-post</link>
      <description><![CDATA[推动 2021 年 meme-stock 狂热的 Reddit 账户于周日发布了在该视频游戏零售商 GameStop Corp. 的 1.16 亿美元持仓信息，随后该股飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/gamestop-s-meme-moment-returns-again-with-gill-s-reddit-post</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 03:10:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
